Package datastructure

Class FeatureAnalysisEntry

java.lang.Object
datastructure.FeatureAnalysisEntry
public final class FeatureAnalysisEntry
extends java.lang.Object
Internal representation of a reference sequence location that is subject to analysis. May represent the full genome, a single gene, contigs or plasmids and chromosomes.

Pairs of instances of this class and SampleAnalysisEntry instances are used internally as so called 'Run entries' to specify a set of analysis tasks, i.e. which sample is analyzed with respect to which specified reference feature.

Since:
2.0
Version:
2.0
Author:
Simon Hackl
